The '''Cult of the Power Droids''' was a religious sect solicited by rogue [[GNK power droid/Legends|GNK power droids]].

==History==
Apparently, a duo of the [[Droid/Legends|droids]] would come to one's door and request funding for this religious fringe group. Advice from renowned linguist [[Ebenn Q3 Baobab/Legends|Ebenn Q3 Baobab]] was that one should merely utter the phrase "Gonk. Gonk. Gonk ko kyenga see," a highly controversial statement that was not allowed to be legally translated (see [[Baobab Security Directive 51-C]]).

